All right, you want to come in here?

16:14.659 --> 16:16.922
No, no, if it's ready, because we're going to talk.

16:17.003 --> 16:21.789
We're going to keep on talking.

16:21.809 --> 16:23.792
Okay, Jenny, just send your name once more.

16:23.812 --> 16:26.496
Oh, it's Jennifer Lee.

16:26.516 --> 16:28.018
Okay.

16:29.260 --> 16:30.161
Good luck.

16:30.862 --> 16:31.002
Thanks.

16:31.825 --> 16:34.308
Thanks so much for everything.

